OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777497070
OL,3,CEurope warming at twice as fast as the
OL,4,Cglobal average, climate report shows
OL,6,FEurope is warming twice as fast as the
OL,7,Fglobal average, according to the
OL,8,Fannual European State of the Climate
OL,9,Freport.
OL,11,FThe report, published on Wednesday,
OL,12,Ffound temperatures in Europe were
OL,13,Fabove average in 95% of areas across
OL,14,Fthe continent last year.
OL,16,FThe UK was among several places,
OL,17,Fincluding Norway and Iceland, to have
OL,18,Ftheir warmest ever year.
OL,20,FMeanwhile Ireland had its second
OL,21,Fwarmest year on record.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
