OL,3,CEurope warming at twice as fast as the
OL,4,Cglobal average, climate report shows
OL,6,FIn July, a heatwave saw temperatures
OL,7,Freach above 30 degrees inside the
OL,8,FArctic circle.
OL,10,FWhite snow and ice reflects some of
OL,11,Fthe sun's heat back but as that melts,
OL,12,Fmore heat is being absorbed instead.
OL,14,FIce is disappearing fast. Greenland's
OL,15,Fice sheet lost 139 gigatons of ice in
OL,16,F2025, which is the equivalent of 100
OL,17,FOlympic swimming pools per minute.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
