OL,3,CEurope warming at twice as fast as the
OL,4,Cglobal average, climate report shows
OL,6,FRenewables supplied nearly half
OL,7,F(46.4%) of Europe's electricity in
OL,8,F2025, almost matching the record level
OL,9,Freached in 2024, with solar power
OL,10,Fsetting a new contribution record, at
OL,11,F12.5%.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
